Package: plinkR
Title: PLINK Command-Line Wrapper for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Huangyi Tang", email = "tang749@purdue.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Execute PLINK/PLINK2 commands from R, capture logs/outputs, and load BED files using a bundled C++ reader adapted from plink2R. Includes bidirectional PLINK <-> BLUPF90 format conversion with automatic allele restoration. Automatically reads report tables from analysis flags.
